      "content": "it's not just the paper though. it's everything. it feels like i'm just running on a treadmill that's going too fast and everyone is watching me fail. i've tried talking to people but it just feels like they don't get it. they just tell me \"it gets better\" but it doesn't feel like it's ever going to. i just feel so tired of fighting it all the time.",
